1、上官网下载安装包，解压到安装目录下 目录下

2、创建快捷方式方法
终端输入：sudo gedit /usr/share/applications/Pycharm.desktop
粘贴模板：
[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=Pycharm
GenericName=Pycharm3
Comment=Pycharm3:The Python IDE
Exec=sh home/dc/xxxx/bin/pycharm.sh
Icon=home/dc/xxxx/bin/pycharm.png
Terminal=pycharm
Categories=Pycharm;

赋予权限：sudo chmod +x idea.desktop


3、设置Pycharm主题
File/setting
主题：appearation

4、安装IDLE
sudo apt-get install idle
